text.tspan: How to sign up for a game on our forums
2. Pick a signup thread (based on size and type)
for other games; look for the ones
that are not FULL or OVER!
3. Reply to the thread, saying "/in" or "I want to play" or something similar
may require a game or two of
usually have more than one game
4. Now just wait for the game to fill and a role PM to appear in your Inbox!
